revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Sector_ChangeSound}}
{{Special|140|tag, newsequence|Sector|Sound}}

* ''tag'': [[Tag]] of affected [[sector]]
* ''newsequence'': Index of new sound sequence

Changes the [[sound sequence]] attached to the sector. This is the same as the one specified by placing one of the [[sound sequence thing]]s (#1400-1411) in a map editor, but with this special the sequence can be changed at run time.
